    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This car is in pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken such incredible care of it, and it's just waiting for a new owner who will love it as much as I have. You really won't find another one this clean. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
