    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I am absolutely thrilled to be listing this total gem. Honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014the paint is sparkling and the interior is completely spotless! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it really shows. It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for someone who will love it as much as I have. You won't find one in better shape than this beauty. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
