    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, a definitive specimen of JDM engineering. This vehicle retains its original 2JZ-GTE twin-sequential turbocharged inline-six, exhibiting perfect compression across all cylinders and zero oil blow-by. The drivetrain features the coveted Getrag V160 six-speed manual transmission, shifting through the gates with factory-new precision, paired with the original Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally immaculate, with all factory VIN tags present and a suspension geometry that remains tight, utilizing original double-wishbone components and OEM bushings. Every vacuum line, seal, and electronic actuator functions within original engineering specifications. This is a rare, unmolested example preserved in concours-level condition, ideal for the purist who values mechanical authenticity and peak performance capabilities.",
